trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.ChildChanged" /> and <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.ChildChanged" /> events.

The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs> class is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> classes when the values of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> properties change.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs> 클래스에서 사용 됩니다는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost> 및 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> 때 클래스의 값은 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 또는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 속성 변경 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs.PreviousChild%2A> property to get the previously assigned child control or element.
trans-unit.target: 사용 된 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs.PreviousChild%2A> 이전에 할당 된 자식 컨트롤 또는 요소를 가져올 속성입니다.

trans-unit.source: The value of the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> property before the new value was assigned.
trans-unit.target: 새 값이 할당되기 전의 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> 속성 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs" /> class.
Gets the value of the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> property before the new value was assigned.
trans-unit.target: 새 값이 할당되기 전의 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> 속성 값을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: The value of the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> property before the new value was assigned.
trans-unit.target: 새 값이 할당되기 전의 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> 속성 값입니다.
